	Note: gnulib macros no longer invoke AC_TYPE_SIZE_T nor
	AC_CHECK_TYPE([ptrdiff_t], , [AC_DEFINE([ptrdiff_t], [long], ...)])
	because we now assume that the system defines size_t and ptrdiff_t.

