	* README, man/iconv_open.3: Add PT154.
	* NOTES: Mention PT154.
	* tests/PT154.TXT: New file.
	* tests/Makefile.in (check): Also test PT154.
	* tests/Makefile.msvc (check): Likewise.
	* tests/Makefile.os2 (check): Likewise.

