	readlink().

	2003-08-24  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>
	* m4/relocatable.m4 (AC_RELOCATABLE): Use $(host) instead of @host@,
	since the substitution of @host@ may occur before the substitution of
	@SET_RELOCATABLE@.

