2003-07-02  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	* m4/lib-ld.m4: Update from GNU gettext.
	* m4/lib-prefix.m4: Update from GNU gettext.
	* m4/gettext.m4: Update from GNU gettext.
	* m4/intmax.m4: New file, from GNU gettext.
