        * src/Makefile.msvc (iconv.obj): Depend on encodings_local.def.
        * src/Makefile.os2 (iconv.obj): Likewise.
        * configure.in: Add tests for locale.h, mbrtowc, wcrtomb, setlocale.
          Recurse into libcharset.
